<table align="center" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" ><tr ><td valign="top" width="455" ><div class="mktEditable" id="left-column" ><p style="color: #000000; font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 16px; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;"><strong>Honeywell is pleased to announce that the 2015 Honeywell Helicopter Operators Conference (HOC) will be held on&nbsp;</strong></span><strong style="font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;">Monday, March 2, 2015 <strong><span>at the Rosen Centre&nbsp;</span></strong>in&nbsp;</strong><strong style="font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;">Orlando, FL. &nbsp;</strong></p>
<p style="vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;"> The conference will provide an overview of the Commercial Helicopter business and include technical briefings on Honeywell propulsion engines, avionics, and safety equipment.</span></p>
<p style="vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;">Representatives from Honeywell&rsquo;s Customer Business Teams, Technical Sales, Marketing &amp; Product Management and Customer &amp; Product Support organizations will be on hand to discuss our latest products and support offerings and share valuable information and experiences through a series of presentations and roundtable discussions.</span></p>
<p style="vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;">A formal invitation to the HOC Customer Reception on March 1, 2015 and link to the HOC registration website will be sent out soon. Please begin to plan accordingly in conjunction with HAI's Heli-Expo Conference scheduled for March 3-5 in Orlando, FL. Information about HAI and local area hotels can be&nbsp;can be found at the <a href="http://heliexpo.rotor.com/" target="_blank">Heli-Expo website</a>.</span></p>
<p style="vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;">Happy Holidays and we look forward to seeing you at the 2015 HOC event!<br /></span></p>
